observe.desc:
[
{As time passes, we change. We may become disabled, lose our minds, be consumed by overwhelming violence or to disappear, to never be seen again.}
]

[
{This portrait captures a moment. It is what we must lose. The employee who sees their own healthy self will unconsciously start to crave. If life can always be like this, if only I can always have a bright smile just like in the portrait.}
]

[
{The employee will start feeling strange. The employee will not get hurt by any damage or attacks. However, other employees will take all the afflicted pain instead.}
]

[
{It was not the self, but the portrait that started becoming increasingly hideous and ugly. The employee eventually stops looking at the portrait and decides to enjoy all the unexpected luck.}
]

[
{But miracles don't last forever. When all the employees that bore the employee's pain and damage perished, it was the employee's turn to die. Once dead, the portrait turned blank.}
]
